<div class="comment-content">
<p>Hello Patrick,<br/>
Can you try the following please and let me know if it works&#8230; (after taking a backup!!!):</p>
<p><code>fart -iC *.html "http://www.domain.org/" \/</code></p>
<p>Note the capital <strong>C</strong> (different from the lower case c &#8211; see the command line switches in my original post) which means that C style characters are permitted in the script. This allows us to use a back slash immediately followed by a forward slash. The backslash escapes the forward slash.</p>
</div> 
</article> 
</li> 
</ol> 
