<div class="comment-content">
<p>Hello Patrick,<br/>
I forgot to mention in my reply to your original comment that I did not actually create this utility <img src="//emtunc.org/blog/wp-includes/images/smilies/simple-smile.png" alt=":)" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;"/><br/>
You will need to escape the quotation marks with back slashes&#8230; like this:<br/>
<code>fart -iC people.html "&lt;code&gt;&lt;a href=\"Site/Map.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;" "&lt;code&gt;&lt;a href=\"/site/map.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;"</code></p>
</div> 
