<div class="comment-content">
<p>Hi, again just to add a little comment.<br/>
Thie command works but as you can see there is a warning.<br/>
<code>fart -C my.txt \\ \/<br/>
Warning: unrecognized character escape sequence: \/<br/>
my.txt<br/>
Replaced 25 occurence(s) in 1 file(s).</code><code></p>
<p>A find a tip : echo %ERRORLEVEL% gives the number of replacements. here 25.</code></p>
</div> 
