<div class="comment-content">
<p>Hey Paul,<br/>
I have not personally tried this but I am sure it is possible.<br/>
One way you could do it (not a very good way I admit) is to have all your possibilities in excel down one column and use that as the input to a FART batch script.<br/>
This is only doable (i.e., requires little work) if the suffix is &#8216;constant&#8217;&#8230; for example, -2, -3, -4, -5 etc.</p>
</div> 
