<div class="comment-content">
<p>Hi,<br/>
Great utility.<br/>
I have a file called prefs.js at location:<br/>
C:\Users\username\AppData\Roaming\Mozilla\Firefox\Profiles\yce2e09c.default</p>
<p>The value of yce2e09c is different in every user profile. </p>
<p> Can I use FART to search file prefs.js in every user profile and replace a line in that file?<br/>
The text I want to change is (&#8220;app.update.auto&#8221;, true) with (&#8220;app.update.auto&#8221;, false) </p>
<p>Please help.</p>
</div> 
